description:
This is a fantastic opportunity for developers and investors to purchase a rarely available DA approved duplex site. Situated in a prime position in the sought after Carbrook area close to the M1 and a short drive to the Bayside. You have a choice with various options to occupy or lease both out. With a high rental yield and sought after location, this makes investment sense. Close to bushland and views to the Riverlakes Golf Course, this is a prime purchase for those looking for a smart investment in a growing area half way between the Gold Coast and Brisbane.

DA approved 2 x three-bedroom duplex's

Save time and money and start building on settlement, no demolition required

Potential rental return per duplex, approximately $580 per week

Contemporary design

Live in one, rent out one

Surrounded by quality homes in a quiet complex

Low body corporate fees

Great schools nearby and minutes to the M1

DA approved plans on request

Opportunities like this rarely become available and the owner will consider all offers!

Contact Jill today for further information.

To be Auctioned on the 5th of February 2023 at Howard Smith Wharves function rooms, if not sold prior.

Disclaimer: The above information is accurate to the best of our knowledge; however, we advise that all interested parties make their own enquiries as we will not be held responsible for any variation that may apply to this information.
